english: Most of the kids have never seen the sea.
chinese: 大多数孩子从未见过大海。

english: The moon is round and bright on that day.
The moon goes around the earth all the time.
chinese: 月亮一直在绕着地球转。

english: We shouldn't leave the rubbish anywhere.
chinese: 我们不应该把垃圾丢在任何地方。

english: We should not cut down too many trees because trees help keep the air clean.
chinese: 我们不应该砍伐太多树木，因为树木有助于保持空气清洁。

english: We use plastic to make bags and bottles, but too much plastic is bad for the earth.
chinese: 我们用塑料制作袋子和瓶子，但太多塑料对地球有害。

english: We should not drive so much because cars use a lot of energy.
chinese: 我们不应该开太多车，因为汽车消耗大量能源。

english: Robots can cheer up sick kids too.
chinese: 机器人也能让生病的孩子开心起来。

english: We're going to see a film about space travel.
chinese: 我们要去看一部关于太空旅行的电影。

english: They will travel to Mars in a time chair.
chinese: 他们将乘坐时间椅前往火星。
